snippet.title: Hellraiser 2 Review w/ Special Guest Adult Film Star Britney Amber
snippet.description:
This week we are covering a sequel in "Hellraiser II" that to this day is still called, "the most brutally original horror sequel in history."  Jamie and I are not Hellraiser experts, but we interviewed one a few months back in Adult Film Star, Actress, and now our resident Hellraiser expert, the incredible Britney Amber. Britney joined in as we discussed being bloody in an all-white house, the Hollywood roaches, Doc Ock, our new fear of mattresses, our love for Kirsty, Pinhead being a pushover, and so much more.  We wouldn't have been able to get through this one without Britney's expertise.

This is a video review that you can watch here sequelsonly.com/hellraiser2
